{"tid":1673430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍在世界軍人運動會作弊 取消比賽資格","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:01:41.000Z","uid":35045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76b8612ddec2c3a4f337386283dbcc984d9011e2","tid":1673430,"uid":35045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191024004324-260417?fbclid=IwAR0VImaKeHKn2e7TWejm8DSqde6nh39baR3Y0Vq0jxZUOhZ0l4h8dIlfqBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20191024004324-260417%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0VImaKeHKn2e7TWejm8DSqde6nh39baR3Y0Vq0jxZUOhZ0l4h8dIlfqBs&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=a171f146\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191024004324-260417?fbclid=IwAR0VImaKeHKn2e7TWejm8DSqde6nh39baR3Y0Vq0jxZUOhZ0l4h8dIlfqBs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年世界軍人運動會(Military World Games 2019)在中國大陸的武漢舉行，時間是10月18日~10月27日。大陸做為地主隊卻爆發嚴重醜聞，解放軍代表隊在「定向運動」(Orienteering)項目被抓到作弊，他們沒使用指南針來找路，而是事前就標好秘密標記，因此被取消比賽資格。<br />\n<br />\n曼谷郵報(Bangkok Post)報導，定向運動是一種尋路的越野賽，參加者在一塊不熟悉的地域，利用主辦單位提供的有限地圖和指南針，找出最快的出路，是一種基礎軍事訓練。在這樣子的比賽中，對於地主國來說當然有巨大的優勢，因此解放軍隊的成績確實相當好，然而評審小組後來發現，所有士兵，都幾乎不需要使用地圖與指南針，而且偏離了預定的直道和窄道。<br />\n<br />\n國際定向越野聯合會（IOF）說，解放軍隊顯然作弊，觀眾為他們指明了方向，並為他們準備了許多「只有他們自己知道的標記」，這賽事被取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「世界軍人運動會」可說是「軍人奧運會」，每四年舉行一次，選手是來自世界各地的軍事運動員，從1995年開始舉辦，首屆主辦地是羅馬，今年已是第7屆，中國大陸對這項賽事頗為重視，特別建了一個選手村，以接待了約1萬參賽的各國士兵、教練和官員。在10月18日的開幕式，國家主席習近平也親自主持。<br />\n<br />\n關於主辦國被抓到作弊並取消資格，大陸國防部並未做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n定向運動並不是今年唯一的大陸運動醜聞，比如今年在波士頓的馬拉松比賽，3名大陸選手因違反規則而被終身禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bangkokpost.com/world/1779084/chinese-orienteering-team-caught-cheating-at-military-world-games?fbclid=IwAR1xOtBInx3TDGyVkmVpTRLmw_lMf1TXILcOx7nsQPWbxiTAX14DNYcfux4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bangkokpost.com%2Fworld%2F1779084%2Fchinese-orienteering-team-caught-cheating-at-military-world-games%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xOtBInx3TDGyVkmVpTRLmw_lMf1TXILcOx7nsQPWbxiTAX14DNYcfux4&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=f0d4e2ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bangkokpost.com/world/1779084/chinese-orienteering-team-caught-cheating-at-military-world-games?fbclid=IwAR1xOtBInx3TDGyVkmVpTRLmw_lMf1TXILcOx7nsQPWbxiTAX14DNYcfux4</a>"},{"pid":"baedf94c8b9c8a605085ec8c2ca57f93a92e68dd","tid":1673430,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=3542dc75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"024a285d156e08d595b8080257e5a8217dcad1da","tid":1673430,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"唔出貓先係新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed961c614bebd08c4ef2a7378251fc502c37cac6","tid":1673430,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0cb7ff86126d7659e378a967137dadbc840224","tid":1673430,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"柒到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dedcfefbf1593adc768423e8bb8e91911344490","tid":1673430,"uid":161988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"Prod"},{"pid":"eb0259c67435844f72a1a411f5610be17b57c63e","tid":1673